description: For sale: $679,999. Stunning Mid Century Modern 4 Bedroom, 4 Bathroom home on over an acre with Bassett Creek winding around two sides of the property. Amazing windows throughout the home that enhance your view of the property and the nature that frames it. Spacious living on all three floors with 4 bedrooms on 2nd level. Dream Master Closet! Updated doors, fixtures, laundry room, wood floors, paint (interior & exterior), base trim, carpet, electrical, and bathrooms. Exciting bonuses include in-ground pool, gazebo, fenced in garden plots and elevator that services all three floors of the home. Within walking distance to Theo Wirth Parkway and Theo Wirth Golf & Ski Area. Minutes to Downtown Mpls and the city lakes.

For sale: $600,000. A rare opportunity in Golden Valley!  Unique, Midcentury Modern home situated on private 1.43 Acre lot w/views of Bassett Creek! Dramatic, vaulted LR w/hardwood floors, stone fireplace and wall of windows w/incredible views. Gourmet Kitchen w/granite countertops, center island w/seating, tile backsplash w/inlaid stone, stainless appliances including gas cooktop, hood, double oven/micro, trash compactor, custom cabinets w/pullout drawers & lighted display areas. Master Brm w/dble closets, custom drawers & shelving. ML handicap accessible, roll-in shower, all living facilities on one level!  Sitting area w/cherry flooring, 4-season porch!  LL FR w/new stacked stone FP, new 3rd Brm + updated bath.  Wet bar with microwave, sink and refrigerator.  Patio door walks out to huge stone patio w/fireplace.  Fenced backyard, storage shed! This home is so unique it needs to be seen to fully appreciate all of the details.  Truly an entertainer's dream or a private retreat close to the City!

For sale: $1,495,000. Paradise found! Five minutes to downtown Minneapolis! Exquisite Kyle Hunt one-story walkout gem with 85' of frontage on magical Hidden (Twin) Lake. This magnificent .75acre forested site is surrounded by Wirth Park and affords total privacy and panoramic lake views. Imagine summers canoeing, kayaking and paddle boarding; skiing Wirth Park and lake trails in the winter; biking and hiking out your door year 'round.  Hidden Lake connects via channel to beautiful Sweeney Lake for additional recreation and fishing. The floor plan, fit & finish are superb, with a luxurious main floor owners' suite and secondary bedrooms on the walkout. Elegant great room and chef's Wolf/Viking kitchen has soaring barrel ceiling, Brazilian walnut floors, fine custom mahogany cabinetry and walls of windows to view wildlife. To-die-for screened porch for sunset entertaining. Family home theatre and game room include a custom wet bar and wine cellar. Rare triple heated garage. Assoc lawn care and snow removal!

For sale: $1,350,000. Welcome to GreenWood Design Build. description:
Recently sold: $692,500. Gorgeous, custom 2-story home built in 2015 sitting on an incredible and rare half acre lot in Golden Valley! Lot is situated at the end of cul-de-sac with no neighbors directly to the right. Back of lot is quite wooded, providing a great additional barrier of privacy in the summertime! 

Insulated and heated garage (32x29) includes hot & cold water access, ceiling fan, attic access & irrigation system controls. Garage door is a 2-stall width, this garage space can easily accommodate 3 parked cars. 

Main floor of home features 9 ft ceilings with 8 ft doors. Upon entering through the front door, there is a flex room/office to the right with grid ceiling. To the left is 1/2 bathroom, mud room with new custom closets (2019 - $5.5K worth) and laundry room with custom made bench & additional storage space. Home is equipped with sound system that also plays out to the covered front porch and back patio area. 

Gourmet kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances: refrigerator, cooktop, wall oven, microwave, range hood, wine cooler & pot filler. OVERSIZED center island (46 in x 90 in / 3.8 feet x 7.5 feet!) with Cambria tops. Custom alder cabinetry, hickory floors & walk-in pantry with motion sensor lighting. 

Dining space is just past kitchen and overlooks the home's beautifully landscaped yard & patio space. 2-sided gas fireplace with brick surround separates dining and great room. Great room features custom, distressed pine cabinetry which complements the room's accent wall wonderfully. 

All 3 bedrooms are on upper level. 2 bedrooms on upper level each have their own walk-in closets and are steps away from the upper level's other full bathroom. 

Master suite has walk-in shower, separate soaking tub, dual vanity & in-floor heated ceramic tile. Master walk-in closet has brand new custom closet shelving (2019). Spectacular view of Minneapolis from this room, especially highlighted at nighttime!

Lower level is completely unfinished -- waiting for the next owner to add their own design and touch to the space and add some instant equity! An egress window is already installed for future 4th bedroom and rough-in for the home's future 4th bathroom is readily accessible. Total basement's unfinished sqft is 1,166 sqft. 

Seller has put nearly $40,000 into landscaping upgrades since home was built. Backyard features a 46 ft x 18 ft paver brick patio, freestanding wood-burning fireplace w/ stone surround, breathtaking waterfall & additional exterior lighting.

Recently sold: $350,000. You will love this charming two bedroom, one bathroom, one story home for sale in Golden Valley with gorgeous gardens, mature tees and beautiful landscaping galore! Located within ISD 281-Robbinsdale School District, close to Rice Lake Park and the Briarwood Nature area and just minutes to Hwy 100 for those who commute!

Enjoy 1,200 finished square feet plus a framed in lower level awaiting your finishing touches! The inviting entrance welcomes you into an open layout in the dining/spacious living room w/large picture window allowing tons of natural light plus a cozy wood fireplace with built-in shelving and secret passage to the porch! The adjoining eat-in kitchen includes a stainless steel fridge/dishwasher, vintage stove and a breakfast bar!  Relax and enjoy peaceful wildlife views in the three season porch with a walkout to the patio--great places to gather with friends and family! The main level also includes two good sized bedrooms and a full bathroom with separate tub/shower!

The unfinished lower level includes a family room w/fireplace, master bedroom, laundry, plumbed/rough-in second bathroom all framed and ready to finish, build equity and increase your square footage!


Additional amenities include: hobby greenhouse, an abundance of perennials, storage shed, attached two car garage plus so much more!
